<section class="hero container">
<h1> Add a new entry to your journal </h1>
</section>

<section class="row">
<div class="grid">
<form action="/trips" method="POST">
<label>Date Camped:</label>
<input type="text" name="trip[date_camped]"><br>
<br>
<label>National Park, Forest, Monument or BLM area:</label>
<input type="text" name="trip[park]"><br>
<br>
<label>Campground Name:</label>
<input type="text" name="trip[campground]"><br>
<br>
<label>Notes:(Optional but encouraged)</label><br>
<p>Feel free to write a brief review of your experience. 
(Love it or hate it? Did the park and/or campground have any special views, amenities, sites, or other features?)</p>
<input type="textarea" name="trip[notes]"><br>
<br>
<p>Select where you would like to store this entry:</p>

<div>
  <input type="radio" id="visited" name="trip[visited]" value="true"
         checked>
  <label for="visited">Already Camped Here/Add to Journal</label>
</div>

<div>
  <input type="radio" id="not_visited" name="trip[visited]" value="false">
  <label for="not_visited">Add to Camping Bucket List</label>
</div>

<input type="submit" value="Submit Entry">
</form>
</div>
</section>


